 \sum_{k=1}^{n} {\left(\frac{nk-1}{n^3}\right) \sin\frac{k}{n}} = \sum_{k=1}^{n} {\left(\dfrac{k}{n^2} - \dfrac{1}{n^3}\right) \sin\frac{k}{n}} = \dfrac{1}{n}\sum_{k=1}^{n} \dfrac{k}{n}\sin\frac{k}{n} - \dfrac{1}{n^3}\sum_{k=1}^{n} \sin\frac{k}{n} 
a=0
b=1
